        "Title": "Sink the Competition",
        "Location": "LOCATION_COASTALTOWN",
        "PublicId": "103505552795",
        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_PRO/Scenes/Missions/CoastalTown/_scene_octopus.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 8ceaba03-05dd-494e-9032-1936cffcdfd0).Image",
        "Description": "Good afternoon, 47. \r\rYour targets are Sebastian Noce and Reginaldo Neglia, two fishermen who seized control of Sapienza’s coastline through sabotage and coercion. Their rise has disrupted a long-standing syndicate, which now seeks retribution. You are to eliminate both men. Discretion is vital. Accidental deaths are preferred. Collateral damage is not. Let their empire sink beneath the surface—quietly, without a ripple.\r\rGood Luck.",
